name: Floral Prom Dress
description:
Get early access to build and test build, be able to try all epochs and test them by yourself on Patreon or contact me for support on Discord

To support me you can buy me a coffe at https://ko-fi.com/antonioriolo

Training settings:

34 images, 20 steps, 13 epochs, you find many epochs (with test images using plot xy script) on my Patreon while supporting me.

Recommended settings:

  • Make sure you are aware on the usage instructions of LORA

  • Sampler: DPM++ SDE Karras (Recommended for best quality, you may try other samplers)

  • CFG Scale : 5 to 9

  • LORA weight for txt2img: reccomended 0.2-0.5. (0.3 gave best results to me)

  • Keys: floral_prom_dress, back view

This model isn't hard to use, just use the main keyword, preferably at the start of your prompt and if necessary with a weight, i used 1.3 as a weight for the keyword in the posted images.

For some of the images i used ControlNet Poses Pack that you can download from my creator page, just search for poses in my model page if you want to replicate these images.

Enjoy!
